00:13:02.030 --> 00:13:03.920
the error code and
debug messages that

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:05.540
are available in the library.

00:13:05.540 --> 00:13:07.730
Instead of returning
a generic error code,

00:13:07.730 --> 00:13:11.510
we now expanded the API to
return specific, granular error

00:13:11.510 --> 00:13:14.360
messages for each
class of exception.

00:13:14.360 --> 00:13:16.550
This change will help you
minimize your debug time

00:13:16.550 --> 00:13:19.617
and get things back up
and running quickly.

00:13:19.617 --> 00:13:21.950
So now that we've covered a
lot of the great new updates

00:13:21.950 --> 00:13:23.562
available in
Billing Library 2.0,

00:13:23.562 --> 00:13:25.520
let's talk about how
we're changing the release

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:29.282
process to make it effortless
to stay up to date.

00:13:29.282 --> 00:13:31.490
We've heard from you that
our current release process

00:13:31.490 --> 00:13:33.560
has some areas for improvement.

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:36.680
First, releases are
ad-hoc and unpredictable.

00:13:36.680 --> 00:13:38.540
This leads to
confusion on when you

00:13:38.540 --> 00:13:40.790
need to be updated to
the latest version.

00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:43.250
Further, there are two ways to
integrate with Play Billing.

00:13:43.250 --> 00:13:45.900
We haven't previously defined
an official best practice.

00:13:45.900 --> 00:13:48.030
So it's hard to know
which one you need to use.

00:13:48.030 --> 00:13:49.850
We know we can do better here.

00:13:49.850 --> 00:13:52.160
That's why starting today,
we're excited to announce

00:13:52.160 --> 00:13:55.070
a predictable, yearly
release cadence.

00:13:55.070 --> 00:13:56.930
Every I/O, starting
with this one,

00:13:56.930 --> 00:14:00.170
will be releasing a new
major version of the library.

00:14:00.170 --> 00:14:03.718
Each release will contain the
latest features and API changes

00:14:03.718 --> 00:14:05.510
to ensure you have
access to everything you

00:14:05.510 --> 00:14:08.822
need to keep your monetization
strategy at the cutting edge.

00:14:08.822 --> 00:14:11.030
We're also announcing that
the Billing Library is now

00:14:11.030 --> 00:14:14.240
the official way to
integrate with Play Billing.

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:16.040
Going forward,
these releases are

00:14:16.040 --> 00:14:18.740
intended to be effortless
to adopt into your app

00:14:18.740 --> 00:14:21.020
by simply updating
to the latest version

00:14:21.020 --> 00:14:23.740
with your build
target each year.

00:14:23.740 --> 00:14:25.520
So you'll know when
updates are coming,

00:14:25.520 --> 00:14:28.130
so you can plan your roadmap
around this predictable

00:14:28.130 --> 00:14:29.300
release.

00:14:29.300 --> 00:14:31.700
Of course, no talk would
be complete without a note

00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:33.020
